headline: Otis Provides The Kross in Ho Chi Minh City With Smart Mobility Systems
summary: Otis (NYSE: OTIS), the world's leading elevator and escalator manufacturing, installation and service company, will install advanced technology and connected vertical mobility solutions for The Kross, a premium 39-story mixed-use building in the heart of Ho Chi Minh's central business district.
